data.description: Experience breathtaking Hill Country views and revel in the unparalleled charm of this exceptional residence. Nestled in Travisso, this remarkable Toll Brothers custom-built home was completed in 2021, boasting a flawless model home appeal. With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and two additional library/office rooms, it offers a perfect blend of functionality and elegance. From the moment you approach the front door, you'll be captivated by the craftsmanship and upscale features that set this home apart. High ceilings, an open floor plan, and a wall-to-wall glass sliding door create an expansive and luminous ambiance. The kitchen seamlessly integrates with the family and dining room, showcasing a generous island, Silestone countertops, stainless steel Whirlpool appliances, an eye-catching marble tile backsplash, 68-inch upper cabinets reaching the ceiling, recessed and pendant lighting. Throughout the home, upgraded ceiling lighting fixtures, and oak hardwood floors add warmth and sophistication, while 8-foot doors and an upgraded French glass door in the dining room elevate the overall aesthetic. The spacious master bedroom provides a sanctuary with its double vanity, garden tub, walk-in shower, and walk-in closet. The house is equipped with a water filtration system and a water softener loop. Imagine the convenience of recharging your electric car while enjoying breathtaking sunsets and hill county views from the covered back porch. Discover a luxurious array of offerings, including a well-equipped workout facility, an inviting pool, scenic walking trails, and tennis courts. Travisso's idyllic setting provides a serene and leisurely lifestyle, while its proximity to restaurants, shopping destinations, and the vibrant attractions of downtown Austin adds an extra layer of convenience. Furthermore, this residence falls within the prestigious LISD school district, ensuring access to top-rated schools.
